Ethnicity and cardiovascular health inequalities in people with severe mental 
illnesses: protocol for the E-CHASM study.

Das-Munshi J(1), Ashworth M(2), Gaughran F(3), Hull S(4), Morgan C(5), Nazroo 
J(6), Roberts A(7), Rose D(5), Schofield P(2), Stewart R(8), Thornicroft G(5), 
